      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d117n1-ptr" id="PJA04d117n1">1</a>
      
   <p>An unacknowledged child.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d117n2-ptr" id="PJA04d117n2">2</a>
      
