     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d117n3-ptr" id="PJA04d117n3">3</a>
      
   <p>Compare the order of events prescribed in <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to John Winthrop, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-04-02-0078" class="document">12 May</a> (above).</p>

